nor time, nor hate's theft<br>can steal your heart from mine.<br>I love you with all my heart and soul.<br>With you I am whole.<br><br>Just for you Merili<br>Hope you enjoy it.<br><br><br>Benidwen <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub76.ezboard.com/ubenidweneq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>BenidwenEQ</A> at: 10/25/01 9:23:01 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub76.ezboard.com/ubenidweneq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>BenidwenEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><b>RA Member</span><br>  Posts: 73<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(10/25/01 9:22:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsmemberinformation.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=244.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Poems to Merili, hope you enjoy.</span><hr size=1> Hey I finished a poem I have been working for a month on and every second of everyday I have thought about you and this is what my poem turned out to be. My English teacher said I have a great talent and said I should send this one. But this one is for you Merili, I hope it describes my love for you.<br><br><br>I know I may not always show it,<br>But you mean the world to me.<br>Deep down inside, I hope you know it,<br>For me, these things don't come naturally.<br><br>Every second we're apart, I long for your touch.<br>I wish you could know how I feel.<br>And though we're not together much,<br>I know what I feel for you is real.<br><br>We've had our share of tough times,<br>However, most people do.<br>As long as the sun continues to shine,<br>We'll keep making it through.<br><br><br>Benidwen  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub76.ezboard.com/brandomacts.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=merili>Merili</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><b>RA Member</span><b